blukii SDK Documentation (Android)

Packages 
Package Description
com.blukii.sdk.cloud
blukii library package for authentication and communication with blukii Manager (https://manager.blukii.com).
com.blukii.sdk.common
blukii library package for common enums and helper classes.
com.blukii.sdk.config
blukii library package for connection based communication with blukii devices.
com.blukii.sdk.config.datatype
blukii library package for config datatypes.
com.blukii.sdk.discovery
blukii library package for discovery of BluetoothLE (BLE) modules.
com.blukii.sdk.info
blukii library package for communication with blukii Manager Info CMS.
